{"tid":2478570,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"曾國衞：組織或煽動投白票等同操縱選舉　會研究規管","createTime":"2021-04-07T07:09:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T09:45:58.000Z","uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"281abbd8e6bdd460ad27afc4692bcc042df3c303","tid":2478570,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T07:09:26.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】政制及內地事務局局長曾國衞指，組織或煽動投白票、廢票有機會影響選舉結果，等同操縱選舉，當局會研究規管。<br />\n<br />\n曾國衞：「投票你可以有選擇權投或不投，但如果有人特別組織或煽動、呼籲人投白票或不投票、投廢票等情況，某程度上這都是嘗試操縱（選舉）。現時法例上即使未有監管，我們也要研究是否需要在法例上有適當作出規管，從而符合人大常委會就附件一及附件二的要求。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=430142\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D430142&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtM2proQWM4oxojYLcFbEfDU%3D&h=e96acfee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D430142&h=071b3fdc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=430142</a>"},{"pid":"8e020080dab4bb3d755e1f58fc33e83a004cb989","tid":2478570,"uid":289946,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T07:11:02.000Z","msg":"助選，拉票，算唔算操控選舉😂😂😂"},{"pid":"c7a09adb9f4c3f0e76b5209c50f3500c38dba414","tid":2478570,"uid":11291,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T07:15:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYbrU6bUjPnenmBXDEJy98zaDoHNdNQaQ4tXpZ2jp7AHr?filename=EnYxwNU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEnYxwNU.jpg&h=9e819357&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"046988bf51b0d930575a6d4123a44b9755999dbf","tid":2478570,"uid":216163,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T07:16:03.000Z","msg":"組織或煽動投民X聯等同操縱選舉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31ed7856ff4ee291514a405505946a3cb1aaf9ae","tid":2478570,"uid":277339,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"re